{"tid":1718044,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"因為你地阻膠為左個光環 我地荃灣一個手足比人斬斷手筋腳筋終身殘廢 一個比人打完掉落樓慘死 你地班冷氣軍師同阻膠滿意未？","createTime":"2019-11-13T17:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T11:04:47.000Z","uid":252492,"like":157,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"d70c32780b3257127c3cf4a0984bda6941dec829","tid":1718044,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:57:52.000Z","msg":"已知都2件 有堆比人打到爆缸<br />\n重未計可能未知既 你睇你班人放過班藍絲製造左咩後果出黎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xN8T19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xN8T19.jpg&h=3a320e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠永遠都唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n佢地永遠唔會care手足比人打到有幾傷<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜 要前線放藍衫走<br />\n結果同一班藍衫轉頭斬斷其他手足手筋腳筋攪到個手足終身殘廢同累其他手足比人打到個頭爆缸<br />\n<br />\n重有依3個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者阻人私了<br />\n班藍絲見出黎打人斬人根本無後果 又有左膠保護 又有黑警保護<br />\n越黎越變本加厲 更加暴力對待我地前線<br />\n<br />\n你班撚樣左膠做過咩？只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話觀感唔好會扣幾多分 會失民意<br />\n<br />\n永遠只敢站係安全地方霸佔道德高地<br />\n根本就唔會理會前線自己友比藍絲打到點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a4802b51b069249404b303a632d7c3d5939ca08a","tid":1718044,"uid":225098,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:58:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，團結！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pn0uDtC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpn0uDtC.jpg&h=4d94e9cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4oPDtC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4oPDtC.jpg&h=3cd8836e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JsWtT1Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJsWtT1Y.jpg&h=04ca0144&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EufuDtD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt